author: NEW YORK DAILY NEWS
title: ‘Daily Show’ host Trevor Noah dating model Jordyn Taylor
text:
“Daily Show” host Trevor Noah is reportedly dating model Jordyn Taylor. Breaking news: Trevor Noah has a hot new romance!
The comedian introduced model Jordyn Taylor as his girlfriend at "The Daily Show" premiere party on Thursday, Us Weekly reports.
Noah met Taylor after moving to New York earlier this year to host the Comedy Central series, according to the site.
The romance is so serious that the couple are said to be living together on the Upper West Side.
Taylor, who works as a model for Ram’s auto shows , hasn't shared photos of them together on social media.
But she has been a cheerleader for her rumored beau, occasionally promoting “The Daily Show” on her accounts.
